'''Gratenite''' was a white stone which was carved from cliffs and could be used in the construction of buildings. It is unknown whether it was a material only to be found on [[Terephon]], where it was the building material of choice in the construction of [[Villa Solis]], [[Galney (Ducha of Terephon)|Ducha Galney's]] private hunting retreat.

